    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel your<strong> garlic </strong>and add it to a <strong>food processor</strong> with your<strong> basil</strong>,<strong> grated Italian hard cheese</strong>,<strong> </strong>3 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[4 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp] </span><strong>cold water</strong>, <strong>blanched peas </strong>and the juice of half your<strong> lemon[s]</strong></p><p>Blitz until well combined and semi-smooth – this is your <strong>pea pesto</strong></p><p>Tip: No food processor? Chop everything up as finely as you can and mix it together!</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
