    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, wash your<strong> salad</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the<strong> salad </strong>to a bowl with a squeeze of <strong>lemon juice </strong>and give everything a gentle mix up – this is your<strong> zingy salad</strong></p><p>Cut the<strong> remaining lemon </strong>into wedges</p>",
